1
00:00:10,039 --> 00:00:11,279
We interrupt with breaking news.

2
00:00:11,560 --> 00:00:14,039
Premier Medical Hall in Chinatown

3
00:00:14,039 --> 00:00:15,320
suffered a tragedy yesterday.

4
00:00:16,120 --> 00:00:17,399
Mom, Dad...

5
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:20,399
For generations, we healed in peace.

6
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:22,839
Then disaster struck and my parents were murdered.

7
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:25,440
I was framed by my fiancée and jailed.

8
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:28,079
Luckily, Young Master Gu watched over my sister.

9
00:00:28,440 --> 00:00:30,239
That gave me some peace of mind in prison.

10
00:00:30,239 --> 00:00:33,000
And uncovered clues to my parents' murder.

11
00:00:35,399 --> 00:00:36,920
Boss, we've got a new guy today.

12
00:00:37,439 --> 00:00:39,640
Really? Then let's lay down the rules.

13
00:00:41,479 --> 00:00:42,359
Sorry, sorry.

14
00:00:42,359 --> 00:00:43,399
Watch where you're going!

15
00:00:43,520 --> 00:00:44,799
Are you blind, you fat piece of trash?

16
00:00:52,679 --> 00:00:54,560
I was just looking for a punching bag.

17
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:55,880
You fat bastard.

18
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:56,600
And you delivered yourself right to me.

19
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:57,119
Stop!

20
00:00:59,039 --> 00:01:01,679
1580, I'm warning you, stay out of this.

21
00:01:01,679 --> 00:01:02,240
Around here,

22
00:01:02,399 --> 00:01:03,359
I call the shots.

23
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:05,480
And what if I insist on butting in?

24
00:01:05,799 --> 00:01:07,280
Then I'll teach you the rules here.

25
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:07,920
Get him!

26
00:01:19,519 --> 00:01:19,959
Boss!

27
00:01:43,719 --> 00:01:45,159
No more bullying newcomers.

28
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,319
That's my rule.

29
00:01:47,319 --> 00:01:48,680
Stop calling me 1580.

30
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,200
My name is Ren Feifan.

31
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:10,479
Dad

32
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:11,599
Mom

33
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,080
Don't worry

34
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:15,759
I won't let any of them get away

35
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,840
Welcome back, Master

36
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,240
Did you find Ren Ran?

37
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:21,639
She's at Zhao Biao's club

38
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,800
They played dirty with Young Master Gu away

39
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:25,879
Let's go

40
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,159
To get her

41
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:27,439
Right

42
00:02:30,599 --> 00:02:32,479
Time to settle all scores with Zhao Biao

43
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:51,960
Where are they?

44
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:54,520
Who's there?

45
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,240
Where the hell did they go?

46
00:02:57,719 --> 00:02:58,240
Who's there?

47
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,560
Get out here!

48
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:07,319
Beat him to death!

49
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,560
Who the hell are you people?

50
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,479
Do you know where this is?

51
00:03:20,159 --> 00:03:21,879
You'll be in big trouble soon.

52
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:23,840
Behave yourself!

53
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:24,719
My boss is Ma Dongxi!

54
00:03:24,719 --> 00:03:25,520
Cut the crap.

55
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:35,800
Ren Ran.

56
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:36,919
It's all right now.

57
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,879
Ren Feifan.

58
00:03:43,039 --> 00:03:43,479
Shut up.

59
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:49,639
Take Ren Ran home first.

60
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:55,120
Ren Feifan, what are you trying to do?

61
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,840
Answer one question for me.

62
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:57,199
I...

63
00:03:57,199 --> 00:03:57,840
Who's there?

64
00:03:57,879 --> 00:03:58,680
Boss.

65
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,159
Who is it?

66
00:03:59,159 --> 00:03:59,879
Who's there?

67
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:00,439
Boss.

68
00:04:00,439 --> 00:04:01,000
Who is it?

69
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,719
Ren Feifan, you're dead!

70
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:07,719
I...

71
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,800
Your name is Ren Feifan?

72
00:04:13,199 --> 00:04:13,800
Yeah.

73
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,960
Were you in North City Prison?

74
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:15,960
Just got out today?

75
00:04:16,319 --> 00:04:16,800
Yes.

76
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:20,000
Benefactor!

77
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,040
Benefactor!

78
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,240
I finally get to meet you!

79
00:04:28,199 --> 00:04:29,680
Back when you were inside,

80
00:04:30,079 --> 00:04:32,560
you saved our family's only heir in three generations!

81
00:04:33,519 --> 00:04:34,079
Look here.

82
00:04:39,319 --> 00:04:39,639
Come on.

83
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,480
The situation isn't looking good.

84
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,560
Ma.

85
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:10,920
Yes.

86
00:05:11,079 --> 00:05:13,759
He's wanted to thank you for saving him inside.

87
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:15,319
We were supposed to pick you up today.

88
00:05:15,399 --> 00:05:17,279
But we missed you. Look at this.

89
00:05:20,279 --> 00:05:21,160
Boss Feifan.

90
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:24,560
From now on, your word is my word.

91
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,879
My turf is your turf.

92
00:05:27,199 --> 00:05:28,319
Just say the word,

93
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:31,120
and we'll go through fire and water for you.

94
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,199
Go through fire and water,

95
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:33,399
without hesitation.

96
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,519
Four years ago,

97
00:05:36,399 --> 00:05:38,199
why did you kill my parents?

98
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:39,319
I...

99
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:41,519
I know someone took the fall for you.

100
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:44,399
A prescription.

101
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:46,399
You don't know medicine or healing.

102
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:47,720
What did you want the prescription for?

103
00:05:48,399 --> 00:05:49,279
I...

104
00:05:50,319 --> 00:05:51,120
Well...

105
00:05:52,079 --> 00:05:53,160
Someone else sent me to do it.

106
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:53,759
Who?

107
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:56,639
Talk, now!

108
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:57,519
No, Boss.

109
00:05:57,959 --> 00:05:58,399
I...

110
00:05:59,199 --> 00:06:00,000
This matter...

111
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,000
Speak!

112
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:05,519
It was the Wang heir, Wang Wenhao.

113
00:06:10,879 --> 00:06:13,759
Not bad. Ten minutes longer than last time.

114
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:20,839
If watching me do it didn't give you an adrenaline rush,

115
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,879
you probably wouldn't even get excited, right?

116
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,439
Useless man.

117
00:06:30,199 --> 00:06:31,120
So boring.

118
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:42,199
President Wang.

119
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:44,680
Ren Feifan is back.

120
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:47,480
And Ma Dongxi has become his underling.

121
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,920
Who could have seen this coming?

122
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:50,680
He nearly beat me to death.

123
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:54,040
President Wang, only you can protect me now.

124
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,199
So you're saying,

125
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,439
you told him everything, didn't you?

126
00:06:58,839 --> 00:06:59,680
No, President Wang.

127
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,120
Look at me.

128
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:05,199
He would've killed me if I didn't talk.

129
00:07:08,439 --> 00:07:10,000
President Wang! President Wang!

130
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:13,240
Four years ago, you botched my job.

131
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:16,560
I told you never to appear before me again.

132
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:19,240
Don't ruin things for me again!

133
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:20,839
Understood?

134
00:08:09,879 --> 00:08:10,519
Ren Feifan!

135
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,480
Feeding your sister random meds again?

136
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:13,800
Stop right there!

137
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,000
Recite it from the beginning.

138
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,680
Ying Zhi Zhuan Ren, Wang Li...

139
00:08:22,319 --> 00:08:23,439
What do you mean, Wang Leehom?

140
00:08:23,439 --> 00:08:24,440
It's Li Fanghong.

141
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,519
Don't just make things up.

142
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:28,159
You got it wrong again! You...

143
00:08:29,279 --> 00:08:30,000
And now you're running?

144
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,639
Feifan,

145
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:55,799
you're finally back.

146
00:08:56,759 --> 00:08:57,600
Brother Hui.

147
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,559
Yeah.

148
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:01,919
After Master and his wife passed away,

149
00:09:01,919 --> 00:09:03,679
Premier Medical Hall was liquidated.

150
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:05,000
Nothing was left behind.

151
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:08,960
Over the years, the Wangs won over the Li Group,

152
00:09:09,279 --> 00:09:11,080
and joined with distributor Xu...

153
00:09:12,639 --> 00:09:13,559
Joined with the Xu Family.

154
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:16,480
These three are now in cahoots.

155
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,799
Through hostile takeovers,

156
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:21,200
they control almost 80% of North City's pharma market.

157
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,919
Other clinics that refused to pick a side

158
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,360
were all pushed out.

159
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,399
North City today

160
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,919
is no longer the North City we knew.

161
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:36,639
I'll make the Wang family

162
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,679
pay blood for blood.

163
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:51,080
Lu Jianqi just became president of the Northern City Medical Association.

164
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,879
We've got to get him on our side.

165
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:55,799
Cut the useless crap.

166
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,519
You think I don't know that?

167
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,720
I've sent gifts twice already.

168
00:10:01,279 --> 00:10:02,159
And they were all sent back.

169
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,279
Dad, just hear me out.

170
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,200
I've already found a way in.

171
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,399
It'll definitely work.

172
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:09,879
I've done my research.

173
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:13,600
Lu Jianqi's father has a severe cataract.

174
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:17,000
I've gathered top experts from home and abroad

175
00:10:17,399 --> 00:10:18,480
to take turns treating him.

176
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:19,919
There's no way we can't cure him.

177
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,279
Will this actually work?

178
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,600
Of course it will.

179
00:10:27,159 --> 00:10:29,440
You're finally using your head this time.

180
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:30,480
Fine.

181
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:31,720
Go handle it.

182
00:10:32,879 --> 00:10:33,639
Don't worry, Dad.

183
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,519
I heard Ren Feifan is back.

184
00:10:39,639 --> 00:10:41,440
That small fry won't last long.

185
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,440
Once I've dealt with Lu Jianqi,

186
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,279
I'll take my time playing with him.

187
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:48,639
The project is at a critical stage right now.

188
00:10:49,519 --> 00:10:50,879
We absolutely can't afford any slip-ups.

189
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:53,919
If you spot any potential threats,

190
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:56,360
best to eliminate them in advance.

191
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,120
Don't worry, Dad.

192
00:10:57,519 --> 00:10:58,240
I know what I'm doing.

193
00:11:05,279 --> 00:11:05,679
Master.

194
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:08,200
Ren Ran has been admitted to the South City sanatorium.

195
00:11:09,039 --> 00:11:09,600
How is she?

196
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:10,720
Is she adjusting well?

197
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,759
Don't worry, I've arranged everything there.

198
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:13,840
Rest assured, Master.

199
00:11:16,679 --> 00:11:19,039
Also, Master, I've delivered what you asked me to.

200
00:11:19,519 --> 00:11:21,039
Lu Jianqi wants to meet you tomorrow to discuss it.

201
00:11:25,639 --> 00:11:26,240
All of you, get away!

202
00:11:26,559 --> 00:11:27,159
Back, back, back!

203
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:27,960
Get away, all of you!

204
00:11:28,519 --> 00:11:29,159
Is that so!

205
00:11:29,639 --> 00:11:32,600
You want to cut into this old man's eyes?

206
00:11:32,879 --> 00:11:33,919
Not in this lifetime!

207
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,960
Mr. Lu, please calm down.

208
00:11:37,879 --> 00:11:39,559
These doctors I invited for you

209
00:11:39,759 --> 00:11:42,519
are all top cataract surgery specialists from home and abroad.

210
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:45,639
It took great effort to bring them here.

211
00:11:46,399 --> 00:11:47,320
Let me ask you just one thing.

212
00:11:47,799 --> 00:11:49,840
Can it be cured without surgery?

213
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,840
I'm Dr. Alexander.

214
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:57,240
I have extensive experience in cataract surgery.

215
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,320
You can trust me.

216
00:11:59,399 --> 00:12:00,960
Get out! What nonsense is this?

217
00:12:01,399 --> 00:12:02,440
Go, go, all of you, leave!

218
00:12:02,799 --> 00:12:03,159
Everyone out!

219
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,200
Out, out, out!

220
00:12:04,399 --> 00:12:04,759
All of you, leave!

221
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:05,799
Get out, now!

222
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,440
Just grab him and do the surgery.

223
00:12:07,559 --> 00:12:07,960
Are you leaving or not?

224
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,480
Once his eyes are healed, he'll thank us.

225
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,039
All of you, get away!

226
00:12:12,039 --> 00:12:12,720
Step back!

227
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,399
Who dares?

228
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:22,000
Dad, Dad, don't get worked up.

229
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:22,799
Please calm down.

230
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:24,120
I'll handle it.

231
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:25,919
President.

232
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,759
I know you're a devoted son,

233
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:31,639
but if we keep delaying his eye treatment,

234
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,480
it really won't be curable.

235
00:12:34,399 --> 00:12:37,120
Cutting into the eyes is no small matter.

236
00:12:39,919 --> 00:12:40,559
Here's what we'll do.

237
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:43,480
If any of you

238
00:12:43,759 --> 00:12:46,960
can carve the word 'Healer' on a single grain of rice,

239
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,840
that person will be qualified to operate on the old man.

240
00:12:49,879 --> 00:12:51,360
Rice? How is that possible?

241
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:53,360
That's indeed asking too much.

242
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,639
If none of you can do it,

243
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:58,919
then please leave.

244
00:13:01,639 --> 00:13:02,360
I can do it.

